&lt;h1 id="study-at-different-places"&gt;Study at different places&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The three pillars of learning; seeing much, suffering much, and studying much.&lt;br&gt;
(Welsh triad; later attributed to Benjamin Disraeli)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;It is a very good idea to do your graduate study at a different institution as your undergraduate study, and to take a postdoctoral position at a different place from where you did your graduate study.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>